INSERT INTO `chat_history` VALUES (393218580902113280,'创建一个个体的团队介绍静态网站。色系：活力橙蓝(#0277bd+#ff6f00)，布局：网格卡片。包含团队愿景Banner、成员卡片网格（含头像占位、姓名、职位、简介）、团队文化价值观、团队数据展示（成员数量、项目经验等）、加入我们招聘区、联系方式。请为团队设计一个 LOGO。页面需有成员卡片悬浮和滚动渐入动效。所有内容使用真实可信的团队场景文本。基于 VUE。\n\n网站需要展示的具体内容：具体的团队信息你自己模拟。','user',393215140335460352,390705603766513664,'2026-03-22 14:51:15','2026-03-22 14:52:43',1),(393219350334574592,'创建一个个体的团队介绍静态网站。色系：活力橙蓝(#0277bd+#ff6f00)，布局：网格卡片。包含团队愿景Banner、成员卡片网格（含头像占位、姓名、职位、简介）、团队文化价值观、团队数据展示（成员数量、项目经验等）、加入我们招聘区、联系方式。页面需有成员卡片悬浮和滚动渐入动效。所有内容使用真实可信的团队场景文本。\n\n网站需要展示的具体内容：添加模拟数据即可。','user',393219349504102400,390705603766513664,'2026-03-22 14:54:18','2026-03-22 14:54:18',0),(393220290739474432,'\n\n<!-- WORKFLOW_START -->\n\n# 🚀 代码生成 Agent 启动\n\n<div class=\'workflow-meta\'>\n\n| 项目 | 信息 |\n|------|------|\n| 产物ID | `393219349504102400` |\n| 生成类型 | **ai_strategy** |\n| 执行模式 | **分布式工作流** |\n| 原始需求 | 创建一个个体的团队介绍静态网站。色系：活力橙蓝(#0277bd+#ff6f00)，布局：网格卡片。包含团队愿景Banner、成员卡片网格（含头像占位、姓名、职位、简介）、团队文化价值观、团队数据展示（... |\n\n</div>\n\n\n\n<!-- WORKFLOW_EXECUTION_START -->\n\n## 📋 工作流执行计划\n\n<div class=\'workflow-steps\'>\n\n**执行阶段:**\n\n1. 🌐 网络资源整理\n2. 🖼️ 图片资源收集\n3. ✨ 提示词智能增强\n4. 🎯 代码类型策略分析\n5. 💻 AI 代码生成\n6. 🔍 代码质量审查\n7. 🏗️ 项目构建部署\n\n</div>\n\n---\n\n\n\n<!-- NODE_START:__START__ -->\n\n### ✅ 工作流初始化\n\n<div class=\'node-result\'>\n\n**⚙️ 工作流初始化**\n\n- ✓ 工作流上下文已创建\n- ✓ 执行参数已配置完成\n- ✓ 准备开始执行各节点任务\n\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- NODE_END:__START__ -->\n\n\n\n<!-- NODE_START:web_resource_organizer -->\n\n### ✅ 网络资源整理已完成\n\n<div class=\'node-result\'>\n\n**🌐 网络资源整理节点**\n\n- ✓ 整理完成：收集到 **2756** 字符的网络资源\n- ✓ 资源类型：文本素材、URL链接等\n- ✓ 状态：已整合到工作流上下文\n\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- NODE_END:web_resource_organizer -->\n\n\n\n<!-- NODE_START:image_collector -->\n\n### ✅ 图片收集已完成\n\n<div class=\'node-result\'>\n\n**🖼️ 图片资源收集节点**\n\n- ✓ 收集完成：获取到 **752** 字符的图片资源信息\n- ✓ 资源来源：AI生成 + 网络搜索\n- ✓ 状态：已准备用于代码生成\n\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- NODE_END:image_collector -->\n\n\n\n<!-- NODE_START:prompt_enhancer -->\n\n### ✅ 提示词增强已完成\n\n<div class=\'node-result\'>\n\n**✨ 提示词增强节点**\n\n- ✓ 增强完成：提示词优化至 **4151** 字符\n- ✓ 增强内容：融合网络资源、图片信息\n- ✓ 质量提升：更精准的代码生成指令\n\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- NODE_END:prompt_enhancer -->\n\n```html\n<!DOCTYPE html>\n<html lang=\"zh-CN\">\n<head>\n    <meta charset=\"UTF-8\">\n    <meta name=\"viewport\" content=\"width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0\">\n    <title>TechFlow 团队 - 以技术为笔，共绘智能未来</title>\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"style.css\">\n    <link rel=\"stylesheet\" href=\"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css\">\n</head>\n<body>\n    <header class=\"header\">\n        <nav class=\"nav\" role=\"navigation\" aria-label=\"主导航\">\n            <div class=\"nav__container\">\n                <div class=\"nav__logo\">\n                    <img src=\"https://dashscope-result-wlcb-acdr-1.oss-cn-wulanchabu-acdr-1.aliyuncs.com/1d/3a/20260322/bf68d313/18f97066-70f2-4ffb-be64-d80c3bb582791938737546.png?Expires=1774248932&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI5tKPD3TMqf2Lna1fASuh&Signature=goMaPlu6nkH8Im6%2BZe45Gw3NCsQ%3D\" alt=\"TechFlow 团队 Logo\" class=\"nav__logo-img\">\n                    <span class=\"nav__logo-text\">TechFlow</span>\n                </div>\n                <ul class=\"nav__menu\">\n                    <li><a href=\"#vision\" class=\"nav__link\">团队愿景</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#members\" class=\"nav__link\">团队成员</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#values\" class=\"nav__link\">团队文化</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#data\" class=\"nav__link\">团队数据</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#join\" class=\"nav__link\">加入我们</a></li>\n                    <li><a href=\"#contact\" class=\"nav__link\">联系我们</a></li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n        </nav>\n    </header>\n\n    <main class=\"main\">\n        <!-- 团队愿景 Banner -->\n        <section id=\"vision\" class=\"banner\" role=\"banner\">\n            <div class=\"banner__container\">\n                <div class=\"banner__content\">\n                    <h1 class=\"banner__title\">以技术为笔，共绘智能未来</h1>\n                    <p class=\"banner__subtitle\">我们是一支扎根中国、服务全球的科技创新团队，致力于用可靠、敏捷、有温度的技术方案，赋能千行百业的数字化转型。</p>\n                </div>\n                <div class=\"banner__image\">\n                    <img src=\"https://img2.baidu.com/it/u=3135374221,1050845483&fm=253&fmt=auto&app=138&f=JPEG?w=500&h=799\" alt=\"团队愿景图\" class=\"banner__img\">\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <!-- 团队成员网格 -->\n        <section id=\"members\" class=\"members\" aria-labelledby=\"members-title\">\n            <div class=\"members__container\">\n                <h2 class=\"section__title\" id=\"members-title\">核心团队成员</h2>\n                <div class=\"members__grid\">\n                    <div class=\"member-card\">\n                        <div class=\"member-card__avatar\">\n                            <img src=\"https://img1.baidu.com/it/u=1723869328,303407295&fm=253&fmt=auto&app=138&f=JPEG?w=681&h=500\" alt=\"林哲远 头像\" class=\"member-card__img\">\n                        </div>\n                        <h3 class=\"member-card__name\">林哲远</h3>\n                        <p class=\"member-card__position\">首席技术官（CTO）</p>\n                        <p class=\"member-card__bio\">华中科大计算机博士，12年AI系统架构经验；主导交付3个省级政务智能平台，获2024年中国信通院\"可信AI系统\"认证。</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"member-card\">\n                        <div class=\"member-card__avatar\">\n                            <img src=\"https://img2.baidu.com/it/u=3093098988,3030447727&fm=253&fmt=auto&app=138&f=JPEG?w=698&h=500\" alt=\"陈思敏 头像\" class=\"member-card__img\">\n                        </div>\n                        <h3 class=\"member-card__name\">陈思敏</h3>\n                        <p class=\"member-card__position\">产品总监</p>\n                        <p class=\"member-card__bio\">前腾讯P8产品经理，专注B端SaaS产品设计；从0到1打造2款行业头部工具，累计服务企业客户超800家。</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"member-card\">\n                        <div class=\"member-card__avatar\">\n                            <img src=\"https://img1.baidu.com/it/u=1473722824,4081445774&fm=253&fmt=auto&app=138&f=JPEG?w=681&h=500\" alt=\"吴昊 头像\" class=\"member-card__img\">\n                        </div>\n                        <h3 class=\"member-card__name\">吴昊</h3>\n                        <p class=\"member-card__position\">高级前端工程师</p>\n                        <p class=\"member-card__bio\">React/Vue双栈专家，GitHub开源项目`GridFlow`维护者（Star 2.4k+）；坚信\"性能即体验，细节即专业\"。</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"member-card\">\n                        <div class=\"member-card__avatar\">\n                            <img src=\"https://img1.baidu.com/it/u=1723869328,303407295&fm=253&fmt=auto&app=138&f=JPEG?w=681&h=500\" alt=\"张薇 头像\" class=\"member-card__img\">\n                        </div>\n                        <h3 class=\"member-card__name\">张薇</h3>\n                        <p class=\"member-card__position\">用户体验设计师</p>\n                        <p class=\"member-card__bio\">中央美院数字媒体硕士，主导完成17个政府/医疗类系统UI重构；坚持\"无障碍设计是底线，不是加分项\"。</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"member-card\">\n                        <div class=\"member-card__avatar\">\n                            <img src=\"https://img2.baidu.com/it/u=3093098988,3030447727&fm=253&fmt=auto&app=138&f=JPEG?w=698&h=500\" alt=\"郑岩 头像\" class=\"member-card__img\">\n                        </div>\n                        <h3 class=\"member-card__name\">郑岩</h3>\n                        <p class=\"member-card__position\">解决方案架构师</p>\n                        <p class=\"member-card__bio\">10年金融+制造业IT集成经验，持AWS/Azure双云架构师认证；擅长将复杂技术转化为客户可感知的价值链。</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <!-- 团队文化价值观 -->\n        <section id=\"values\" class=\"values\" aria-labelledby=\"values-title\">\n            <div class=\"values__container\">\n                <h2 class=\"section__title\" id=\"values-title\">团队文化价值观</h2>\n                <div class=\"values__grid\">\n                    <div class=\"value-card\">\n                        <i class=\"value-card__icon fas fa-check-circle\"></i>\n                        <h3 class=\"value-card__title\">务实创新</h3>\n                        <p class=\"value-card__desc\">拒绝PPT技术，每个功能上线前必经3轮真实场景压力测试</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"value-card\">\n                        <i class=\"value-card__icon fas fa-users\"></i>\n                        <h3 class=\"value-card__title\">客户共研</h3>\n                        <p class=\"value-card__desc\">需求确认阶段即邀请客户进入敏捷迭代流程，共同定义MVP</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"value-card\">\n                        <i class=\"value-card__icon fas fa-book-open\"></i>\n                        <h3 class=\"value-card__title\">知识平权</h3>\n                        <p class=\"value-card__desc\">内部技术文档100%开源，新人入职7天内可独立提交PR</p>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"value-card\">\n                        <i class=\"value-card__icon fas fa-hourglass-half\"></i>\n                        <h3 class=\"value-card__title\">长期主义</h3>\n                        <p class=\"value-card__desc\">核心成员平均司龄5.2年，技术债清理率连续3年超92%</p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <!-- 团队数据展示 -->\n        <section id=\"data\" class=\"stats\" aria-labelledby=\"stats-title\">\n            <div class=\"stats__container\">\n                <h2 class=\"section__title\" id=\"stats-title\">团队实力数据</h2>\n                <div class=\"stats__grid\">\n                    <div class=\"stat-item\">\n                        <div class=\"stat-item__number\">32人</div>\n                        <div class=\"stat-item__label\">成员规模</div>\n                        <div class=\"stat-item__desc\">含研发22人、设计4人、交付6人（无外包）</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"stat-item\">\n                        <div class=\"stat-item__number\">156+</div>\n                        <div class=\"stat-item__label\">项目经验</div>\n                        <div class=\"stat-item__desc\">覆盖金融、政务、医疗、制造4大领域（2021–2025）</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"stat-item\">\n                        <div class=\"stat-item__number\">41个</div>\n                        <div class=\"stat-item__label\">年度交付</div>\n                        <div class=\"stat-item__desc\">平均交付周期8.7周，客户终验一次性通过率96.3%</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"stat-item\">\n                        <div class=\"stat-item__number\">23项</div>\n                        <div class=\"stat-item__label\">技术沉淀</div>\n                        <div class=\"stat-item__desc\">其中发明专利17项（含3项AI模型优化核心专利）</div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"stat-item\">\n                        <div class=\"stat-item__number\">12个</div>\n                        <div class=\"stat-item__label\">开源贡献</div>\n                        <div class=\"stat-item__desc\">GitHub Star总数18,700+，被Apache Flink等顶级项目引用</div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <!-- 加入我们 -->\n        <section id=\"join\" class=\"join\" aria-labelledby=\"join-title\">\n            <div class=\"join__container\">\n                <h2 class=\"section__title\" id=\"join-title\">加入我们</h2>\n                <div class=\"join__content\">\n                    <h3 class=\"join__subtitle\">寻找同频的「造浪者」，而非追随者</h3>\n                    <p class=\"join__text\">我们不招聘\"完美简历\"，而寻找：</p>\n                    <ul class=\"join__requirements\">\n                        <li class=\"join__requirement\"><i class=\"fas fa-check-circle\"></i> 能把复杂问题拆解成可执行任务的<strong>结构化思维者</strong></li>\n                        <li class=\"join__requirement\"><i class=\"fas fa-check-circle\"></i> 在技术讨论中敢于说\"这个方案有风险\"的<strong>坦诚协作者</strong></li>\n                        <li class=\"join__requirement\"><i class=\"fas fa-check-circle\"></i> 愿意花2小时帮新人调试环境的<strong>知识布道者</strong></li>\n                    </ul>\n                    <div class=\"join__positions\">\n                        <h4 class=\"join__positions-title\">当前开放岗位：</h4>\n                        <p class=\"join__positions-list\">全栈开发工程师｜AI算法研究员｜交付实施顾问</p>\n                        <p class=\"join__positions-link\">详情见 <a href=\"https://careers.example.com\" target=\"_blank\">careers.example.com</a></p>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n\n        <!-- 联系方式 -->\n        <section id=\"contact\" class=\"contact\" aria-labelledby=\"contact-title\">\n            <div class=\"contact__container\">\n                <h2 class=\"section__title\" id=\"contact-title\">联系我们</h2>\n                <div class=\"contact__info\">\n                    <div class=\"contact__item\">\n                        <i class=\"contact__icon fas fa-map-marker-alt\"></i>\n                        <div class=\"contact__detail\">\n                            <h4 class=\"contact__label\">地址</h4>\n                            <p class=\"contact__text\">杭州市西湖区云栖小镇·数智谷A座12F（访客需预约）</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"contact__item\">\n                        <i class=\"contact__icon fas fa-envelope\"></i>\n                        <div class=\"contact__detail\">\n                            <h4 class=\"contact__label\">邮箱</h4>\n                            <p class=\"contact__text\">hello@techflow.team（24小时内人工回复）</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"contact__item\">\n                        <i class=\"contact__icon fas fa-phone\"></i>\n                        <div class=\"contact__detail\">\n                            <h4 class=\"contact__label\">电话</h4>\n                            <p class=\"contact__text\">+86 571 88XXXXXX（工作日 9:00–18:00）</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                    <div class=\"contact__item\">\n                        <i class=\"contact__icon fab fa-weixin\"></i>\n                        <div class=\"contact__detail\">\n                            <h4 class=\"contact__label\">公众号</h4>\n                            <p class=\"contact__text\">TechFlow 团队（获取技术白皮书 & 招聘动态）</p>\n                        </div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n        </section>\n    </main>\n\n    <footer class=\"footer\">\n        <div class=\"footer__container\">\n            <div class=\"footer__logo\">\n                <img src=\"https://dashscope-result-wlcb-acdr-1.oss-cn-wulanchabu-acdr-1.aliyuncs.com/1d/3a/20260322/bf68d313/18f97066-70f2-4ffb-be64-d80c3bb582791938737546.png?Expires=1774248932&OSSAccessKeyId=LTAI5tKPD3TMqf2Lna1fASuh&Signature=goMaPlu6nkH8Im6%2BZe45Gw3NCsQ%3D\" alt=\"TechFlow 团队 Logo\" class=\"footer__logo-img\">\n                <span class=\"footer__logo-text\">TechFlow</span>\n            </div>\n            <p class=\"footer__copyright\">&copy; 2025 TechFlow 团队. 保留所有权利.</p>\n        </div>\n    </footer>\n\n    <script src=\"script.js\"></script>\n</body>\n</html>\n```\n\n```css\n/* style.css */\n:root {\n  --primary-blue: #0277bd;\n  --accent-orange: #ff6f00;\n  --light-gray: #f5f5f5;\n  --medium-gray: #e0e0e0;\n  --dark-gray: #666666;\n  --text-dark: #333333;\n  --white: #ffffff;\n  --shadow-light: 0 2px 8px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);\n  --shadow-medium: 0 4px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);\n  --shadow-hover: 0 12px 24px rgba(255, 111, 0, 0.15);\n  --border-radius: 8px;\n  --transition-fast: 0.2s ease;\n  --transition-medium: 0.3s ease;\n  --transition-slow: 0.5s ease;\n}\n\n* {\n  margin: 0;\n  padding: 0;\n  box-sizing: border-box;\n}\n\nbody {\n  font-family: \'Segoe UI\', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;\n  line-height: 1.6;\n  color: var(--text-dark);\n  background-color: var(--white);\n}\n\n.header {\n  background-color: var(--white);\n  box-shadow: var(--shadow-light);\n  position: sticky;\n  top: 0;\n  z-index: 1000;\n}\n\n.nav {\n  max-width: 1200px;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n  padding: 1rem 2rem;\n}\n\n.nav__container {\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  align-items: center;\n}\n\n.nav__logo {\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 0.5rem;\n}\n\n.nav__logo-img {\n  height: 40px;\n  width: auto;\n}\n\n.nav__logo-text {\n  font-size: 1.5rem;\n  font-weight: bold;\n  color: var(--primary-blue);\n}\n\n.nav__menu {\n  display: flex;\n  list-style: none;\n  gap: 2rem;\n}\n\n.nav__link {\n  text-decoration: none;\n  color: var(--text-dark);\n  font-weight: 500;\n  transition: var(--transition-fast);\n  padding: 0.5rem 0;\n  position: relative;\n}\n\n.nav__link:hover {\n  color: var(--primary-blue);\n}\n\n.nav__link::after {\n  content: \'\';\n  position: absolute;\n  bottom: 0;\n  left: 0;\n  width: 0;\n  height: 2px;\n  background-color: var(--primary-blue);\n  transition: var(--transition-fast);\n}\n\n.nav__link:hover::after {\n  width: 100%;\n}\n\n.main {\n  min-height: calc(100vh - 120px);\n}\n\n.banner {\n  background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--primary-blue), #01579b);\n  color: var(--white);\n  padding: 4rem 2rem;\n  text-align: center;\n}\n\n.banner__container {\n  max-width: 1200px;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n  gap: 3rem;\n  align-items: center;\n}\n\n.banner__title {\n  font-size: 2.5rem;\n  margin-bottom: 1rem;\n  animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease;\n}\n\n.banner__subtitle {\n  font-size: 1.2rem;\n  opacity: 0.9;\n  max-width: 600px;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n  animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease 0.2s both;\n}\n\n.banner__image {\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: center;\n}\n\n.banner__img {\n  max-width: 100%;\n  height: auto;\n  border-radius: var(--border-radius);\n  box-shadow: var(--shadow-medium);\n  animation: fadeIn 0.8s ease 0.4s both;\n}\n\n.section__title {\n  font-size: 2rem;\n  text-align: center;\n  margin-bottom: 3rem;\n  color: var(--text-dark);\n  position: relative;\n}\n\n.section__title::after {\n  content: \'\';\n  position: absolute;\n  bottom: -10px;\n  left: 50%;\n  transform: translateX(-50%);\n  width: 60px;\n  height: 3px;\n  background-color: var(--accent-orange);\n}\n\n.members {\n  padding: 5rem 2rem;\n  background-color: var(--light-gray);\n}\n\n.members__container {\n  max-width: 1200px;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n}\n\n.members__grid {\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));\n  gap: 2rem;\n  margin-top: 2rem;\n}\n\n.member-card {\n  background-color: var(--white);\n  border-radius: var(--border-radius);\n  padding: 2rem;\n  text-align: center;\n  box-shadow: var(--shadow-light);\n  transition: var(--transition-medium);\n  opacity: 0;\n  transform: translateY(30px);\n  animation: slideIn 0.6s ease forwards;\n}\n\n.member-card:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }\n.member-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }\n.member-card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }\n.member-card:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }\n.member-card:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }\n\n.member-card:hover {\n  transform: translateY(-8px);\n  box-shadow: var(--shadow-hover);\n}\n\n.member-card__avatar {\n  width: 120px;\n  height: 120px;\n  margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;\n  border-radius: 50%;\n  overflow: hidden;\n  border: 4px solid var(--primary-blue);\n}\n\n.member-card__img {\n  width: 100%;\n  height: 100%;\n  object-fit: cover;\n}\n\n.member-card__name {\n  font-size: 1.4rem;\n  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n  color: var(--primary-blue);\n}\n\n.member-card__position {\n  font-size: 1rem;\n  color: var(--dark-gray);\n  margin-bottom: 1rem;\n  font-weight: 500;\n}\n\n.member-card__bio {\n  font-size: 0.95rem;\n  color: var(--dark-gray);\n  line-height: 1.6;\n}\n\n.values {\n  padding: 5rem 2rem;\n  background-color: var(--white);\n}\n\n.values__container {\n  max-width: 1200px;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n}\n\n.values__grid {\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n  gap: 2rem;\n  margin-top: 2rem;\n}\n\n.value-card {\n  background-color: var(--light-gray);\n  border-radius: var(--border-radius);\n  padding: 2rem;\n  text-align: center;\n  transition: var(--transition-medium);\n  opacity: 0;\n  transform: translateY(30px);\n  animation: slideIn 0.6s ease forwards;\n}\n\n.value-card:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }\n.value-card:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }\n.value-card:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }\n.value-card:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }\n\n.value-card:hover {\n  transform: translateY(-5px);\n  box-shadow: var(--shadow-medium);\n}\n\n.value-card__icon {\n  font-size: 2.5rem;\n  color: var(--primary-blue);\n  margin-bottom: 1rem;\n}\n\n.value-card__title {\n  font-size: 1.3rem;\n  margin-bottom: 1rem;\n  color: var(--text-dark);\n}\n\n.value-card__desc {\n  font-size: 0.95rem;\n  color: var(--dark-gray);\n  line-height: 1.6;\n}\n\n.stats {\n  padding: 5rem 2rem;\n  background: linear-gradient(to right, var(--primary-blue), #1976d2);\n  color: var(--white);\n}\n\n.stats__container {\n  max-width: 1200px;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n}\n\n.stats__grid {\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));\n  gap: 2rem;\n  margin-top: 2rem;\n}\n\n.stat-item {\n  text-align: center;\n  padding: 2rem;\n  background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);\n  border-radius: var(--border-radius);\n  backdrop-filter: blur(10px);\n  opacity: 0;\n  transform: translateY(30px);\n  animation: slideIn 0.6s ease forwards;\n}\n\n.stat-item:nth-child(1) { animation-delay: 0.1s; }\n.stat-item:nth-child(2) { animation-delay: 0.2s; }\n.stat-item:nth-child(3) { animation-delay: 0.3s; }\n.stat-item:nth-child(4) { animation-delay: 0.4s; }\n.stat-item:nth-child(5) { animation-delay: 0.5s; }\n\n.stat-item__number {\n  font-size: 2.5rem;\n  font-weight: bold;\n  color: var(--accent-orange);\n  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n}\n\n.stat-item__label {\n  font-size: 1.2rem;\n  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n  font-weight: 500;\n}\n\n.stat-item__desc {\n  font-size: 0.9rem;\n  opacity: 0.9;\n  line-height: 1.5;\n}\n\n.join {\n  padding: 5rem 2rem;\n  background-color: var(--light-gray);\n}\n\n.join__container {\n  max-width: 800px;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n  text-align: center;\n}\n\n.join__subtitle {\n  font-size: 1.5rem;\n  color: var(--primary-blue);\n  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n}\n\n.join__text {\n  font-size: 1.1rem;\n  margin-bottom: 1.5rem;\n  color: var(--text-dark);\n}\n\n.join__requirements {\n  list-style: none;\n  margin-bottom: 2rem;\n  text-align: left;\n}\n\n.join__requirement {\n  margin-bottom: 1rem;\n  font-size: 1rem;\n  color: var(--dark-gray);\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 0.5rem;\n}\n\n.join__requirement i {\n  color: var(--accent-orange);\n}\n\n.join__positions {\n  background-color: var(--white);\n  padding: 2rem;\n  border-radius: var(--border-radius);\n  box-shadow: var(--shadow-light);\n}\n\n.join__positions-title {\n  font-size: 1.2rem;\n  color: var(--text-dark);\n  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n}\n\n.join__positions-list {\n  font-size: 1rem;\n  color: var(--dark-gray);\n  margin-bottom: 0.5rem;\n}\n\n.join__positions-link {\n  font-size: 0.9rem;\n  color: var(--primary-blue);\n}\n\n.contact {\n  padding: 5rem 2rem;\n  background-color: var(--white);\n}\n\n.contact__container {\n  max-width: 800px;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n}\n\n.contact__info {\n  display: grid;\n  grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(250px, 1fr));\n  gap: 2rem;\n  margin-top: 2rem;\n}\n\n.contact__item {\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: flex-start;\n  gap: 1rem;\n}\n\n.contact__icon {\n  font-size: 1.5rem;\n  color: var(--primary-blue);\n  min-width: 24px;\n}\n\n.contact__detail {\n  flex: 1;\n}\n\n.contact__label {\n  font-size: 1rem;\n  font-weight: 500;\n  margin-bottom: 0.25rem;\n  color: var(--text-dark);\n}\n\n.contact__text {\n  font-size: 0.95rem;\n  color: var(--dark-gray);\n  line-height: 1.5;\n}\n\n.footer {\n  background-color: var(--text-dark);\n  color: var(--white);\n  padding: 2rem;\n  text-align: center;\n}\n\n.footer__container {\n  max-width: 1200px;\n  margin: 0 auto;\n  display: flex;\n  justify-content: space-between;\n  align-items: center;\n  flex-wrap: wrap;\n  gap: 1rem;\n}\n\n.footer__logo {\n  display: flex;\n  align-items: center;\n  gap: 0.5rem;\n}\n\n.footer__logo-img {\n  height: 30px;\n  width: auto;\n}\n\n.footer__logo-text {\n  font-size: 1.2rem;\n  font-weight: bold;\n}\n\n.footer__copyright {\n  font-size: 0.9rem;\n  opacity: 0.8;\n}\n\n/* 动画效果 */\n@keyframes fadeIn {\n  from {\n    opacity: 0;\n  }\n  to {\n    opacity: 1;\n  }\n}\n\n@keyframes fadeInUp {\n  from {\n    opacity: 0;\n    transform: translateY(30px);\n  }\n  to {\n    opacity: 1;\n    transform: translateY(0);\n  }\n}\n\n@keyframes slideIn {\n  to {\n    opacity: 1;\n    transform: translateY(0);\n  }\n}\n\n/* 响应式设计 */\n@media (max-width: 768px) {\n  .nav {\n    padding: 1rem;\n  }\n  \n  .nav__container {\n    flex-direction: column;\n    gap: 1rem;\n  }\n  \n  .nav__menu {\n    flex-wrap: wrap;\n    justify-content: center;\n    gap: 1rem;\n  }\n  \n  .banner__container {\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n  \n  .banner__title {\n    font-size: 2rem;\n  }\n  \n  .members,\n  .values,\n  .stats,\n  .join,\n  .contact {\n    padding: 3rem 1rem;\n  }\n  \n  .section__title {\n    font-size: 1.8rem;\n  }\n  \n  .member-card,\n  .value-card,\n  .stat-item {\n    padding: 1.5rem;\n  }\n  \n  .member-card__name {\n    font-size: 1.2rem;\n  }\n  \n  .footer__container {\n    flex-direction: column;\n    text-align: center;\n  }\n}\n\n@media (min-width: 768px) and (max-width: 1024px) {\n  .banner__container {\n    grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;\n  }\n  \n  .members__grid {\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);\n  }\n}\n```\n\n```javascript\n\'use strict\';\n\ndocument.addEventListener(\'DOMContentLoaded\', function() {\n    // 平滑滚动导航\n    const navLinks = document.querySelectorAll(\'.nav__link\');\n    \n    navLinks.forEach(link => {\n        link.addEventListener(\'click\', function(e) {\n            e.preventDefault();\n            const targetId = this.getAttribute(\'href\');\n            const targetSection = document.querySelector(targetId);\n            \n            if (targetSection) {\n                window.scrollTo({\n                    top: targetSection.offsetTop - 80,\n                    behavior: \'smooth\'\n                });\n            }\n        });\n    });\n\n    // 滚动动画触发\n    const observerOptions = {\n        threshold: 0.1,\n        rootMargin: \'0px 0px -50px 0px\'\n    };\n\n    const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {\n        entries.forEach(entry => {\n            if (entry.isIntersecting) {\n                entry.target.style.animationPlayState = \'running\';\n                observer.unobserve(entry.target);\n            }\n        });\n    }, observerOptions);\n\n    // 观察需要动画的元素\n    const animatedElements = document.querySelectorAll(\'.member-card, .value-card, .stat-item\');\n    animatedElements.forEach(el => {\n        observer.observe(el);\n    });\n\n    // 导航栏高亮\n    const sections = document.querySelectorAll(\'section[id]\');\n    \n    window.addEventListener(\'scroll\', () => {\n        let current = \'\';\n        \n        sections.forEach(section => {\n            const sectionTop = section.offsetTop;\n            const sectionHeight = section.clientHeight;\n            \n            if (pageYOffset >= (sectionTop - 100)) {\n                current = section.getAttribute(\'id\');\n            }\n        });\n\n        navLinks.forEach(link => {\n            link.classList.remove(\'active\');\n            if (link.getAttribute(\'href\') === `#${current}`) {\n                link.classList.add(\'active\');\n            }\n        });\n    });\n\n    // 悬停效果增强\n    const cards = document.querySelectorAll(\'.member-card, .value-card\');\n    cards.forEach(card => {\n        card.addEventListener(\'mouseenter\', function() {\n            this.style.transform = \'translateY(-8px)\';\n        });\n        \n        card.addEventListener(\'mouseleave\', function() {\n            this.style.transform = \'translateY(0)\';\n        });\n    });\n\n    // 滚动进度指示器（可选功能）\n    const createScrollIndicator = () => {\n        const indicator = document.createElement(\'div\');\n        indicator.style.position = \'fixed\';\n        indicator.style.top = \'0\';\n        indicator.style.left = \'0\';\n        indicator.style.width = \'0%\';\n        indicator.style.height = \'3px\';\n        indicator.style.backgroundColor = \'var(--accent-orange)\';\n        indicator.style.zIndex = \'9999\';\n        indicator.style.transition = \'width 0.1s ease\';\n        document.body.appendChild(indicator);\n\n        window.addEventListener(\'scroll\', () => {\n            const scrollTop = window.pageYOffset;\n            const docHeight = document.body.offsetHeight;\n            const winHeight = window.innerHeight;\n            const scrollPercent = scrollTop / (docHeight - winHeight);\n            const scrollPercentRounded = Math.round(scrollPercent * 100) / 100;\n            indicator.style.width = `${scrollPercentRounded * 100}%`;\n        });\n    };\n\n    // 创建滚动进度指示器\n    createScrollIndicator();\n\n    // 页面加载完成后添加延迟动画\n    setTimeout(() => {\n        const bannerContent = document.querySelector(\'.banner__content\');\n        if (bannerContent) {\n            bannerContent.style.opacity = \'1\';\n            bannerContent.style.transform = \'translateY(0)\';\n        }\n    }, 100);\n});\n```\n\n<!-- NODE_START:ai_code_generator_type_strategy -->\n\n### ✅ 代码生成类型策略已完成\n\n<div class=\'node-result\'>\n\n**🎯 代码类型策略节点**\n\n- ✓ 策略确定：选择 **multi_file** 生成模式\n- ✓ AI分析：基于需求自动选择最优方案\n- ✓ 准备就绪：开始代码生成流程\n\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- NODE_END:ai_code_generator_type_strategy -->\n\n\n\n<!-- NODE_START:code_gene