t-metric\">✅ 会员复购率环比提升8%</div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div class=\"achievement-card\">\n                        <div class=\"achievement-title\"><i class=\"fas fa-users\"></i> KOL合作拓展</div>\n                        <div class=\"achievement-content\">推动与3家头部KOL达成深度合作，制定内容共创计划</div>\n                        <div class=\"achievement-metric\">✅ 带来新增用户5万人</div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div class=\"achievement-card\">\n                        <div class=\"achievement-title\"><i class=\"fas fa-home\"></i> 首页改版项目</div>\n                        <div class=\"achievement-content\">完成首页视觉与功能全面升级，优化用户购物路径</div>\n                        <div class=\"achievement-metric\">✅ 重点品类曝光提升25%</div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div class=\"achievement-card\">\n                        <div class=\"achievement-title\"><i class=\"fas fa-chalkboard-teacher\"></i> 团队能力提升</div>\n                        <div class=\"achievement-content\">组织2场客服团队专项培训，优化服务话术与转化流程</div>\n                        <div class=\"achievement-metric\">✅ 客服转化率提升10%</div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div class=\"achievement-card\">\n                        <div class=\"achievement-title\"><i class=\"fas fa-search\"></i> 竞品分析与策略</div>\n                        <div class=\"achievement-content\">完成主要竞争对手深度分析，识别市场机会与风险点</div>\n                        <div class=\"achievement-metric\">✅ 制定下阶段精细化定价策略</div>\n                    </div>\n\n                    <div class=\"achievement-card\">\n                        <div class=\"achievement-title\"><i class=\"fas fa-truck\"></i> 供应链协同</div>\n                        <div class=\"achievement-content\">强化供应链管理，建立爆款商品库存预警机制</div>\n                        <div class=\"achievement-metric\">✅ 爆款库存充足，售罄率控制在90%</div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"summary-card\">\n                <h2 class=\"section-title\">关键数据表现</h2>\n    