                   <img src=\"https://img0.baidu.com/it/u=105721740,3183919129&fm=253&fmt=auto&app=138&f=JPEG?w=894&h=500\" alt=\"团队协作场景\">\n                        <div class=\"image-caption\">团队培训与协作场景</div>\n                    </div>\n                </div>\n            </div>\n\n            <!-- Company Logo -->\n            <div class=\"summary-card\" style=\"text-align: center;\">\n                <img src=\"https://rich-tams.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/richcodeweaver/2026/03/27/19ea7a78bcec4b349b769e27e36a22d5.png\" alt=\"公司Logo\" style=\"height: 80px; margin: 20px auto; opacity: 0.8;\">\n            </div>\n\n            <div class=\"summary-card\">\n                <h2 class=\"section-title\">下周工作计划</h2>\n                <ul class=\"plan-list\">\n                    <li>持续监控618大促销售数据，及时调整策略</li>\n                    <li>推进会员日活动效果复盘与迭代优化</li>\n                    <li>启动Q3营销规划前期调研工作</li>\n                    <li>完善KOL合作效果评估体系</li>\n                    <li>组织团队分享会，沉淀618大促经验</li>\n                </ul>\n            </div>\n        </main>\n\n        <footer class=\"footer\">\n            <p>制作人：[您的姓名] | 日期：2024年6月7日</p>\n            <p class=\"footer__version\">本报告数据截至2024年6月7日，所有指标均基于内部系统统计</p>\n        </footer>\n    </div>\n\n    <script>\n        // Add smooth hover effects and animations\n        document.addEventListener(\'DOMContentLoaded\', function() {\n            // Add animation to achievement cards on scroll\n            const observerOptions = {\n                threshold: 0.1,\n                rootMargin: \'0px 0px -50px 0px\'\n            };\n\n            const observer = new IntersectionObserver((entries) => {\n                entries.forEach(entry => {\n                    if (entry.isIntersecting) {\n                        entry.target.style.opacity = \'1\';\n                        entry.target.style.transform = \'translateY(0)\';\n                    }\n                });\n            }, observerOptions);\n\n            const achievementCards = document.querySelectorAll(\'.achievement-card\');\n            achievementCards.forEach(card => {\n                card.style.opacity = \'0\';\n                card.style.transform = \'translateY(20px)\';\n                card.style.transition = \'opacity 0.6s ease, transform 0.6s ease\';\n                observer.observe(card);\n            });\n\n            // Add click effect to figure cards\n            const figureCards = document.querySelectorAll(\'.figure-card\');\n            figureCards.forEach(card => {\n                card.addEventListener(\'click\', function() {\n                    this.style.transform = \'scale(1.05)\';\n                    setTimeout(() => {\n                        this.style.transform = \'scale(1)\';\n                    }, 200);\n                });\n            });\n        });\n\n        // Update current date in footer\n        function updateCurrentDate() {\n            const now = new Date();\n            const options = { year: \'numeric\', month: \'long\', day: \'numeric\' };\n            document.getElementById(\'current-date\').textContent = now.toLocaleDateString(\'zh-CN\', options);\n        }\n\n        // Initialize\n        updateCurrentDate();\n        setInterval(updateCurrentDate, 60000); // Update every minute\n    </script>\n</body>\n</html>\n```\n\n<!-- NODE_START:ai_code_generator_type_strategy -->\n\n### ✅ 代码生成类型策略已完成\n\n<div class=\'node-result\'>\n\n**🎯 代码类型策略节点**\n\n- ✓ 策略确定：选择 **single_html** 生成模式\n- ✓ AI分析：基于需求自动选择最优方案\n- ✓ 准备就绪：开始代码生成流程\n\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- NODE_END:ai_code_generator_type_strategy -->\n\n\n\n<!-- NODE_START:code_generator -->\n\n### ✅ AI 代码生成已完成\n\n<div class=\'node-result\'>\n\n**💻 AI 代码生成节点**\n\n- ✓ 生成完成：代码已输出\n- ✓ 输出路径：`E:\\AAA_idea_java\\RichCodeWeaver/appCode/code_output/single_html_395002924146741248`\n- ✓ 下一步：等待 AI 代码质量审查\n\n> 🔍 正在启动代码审查流程...\n\n\n</div>\n\n<!-- NODE_END:code_generator -->\n\n\n\n<!-- NODE_START:ai_code_reviewer -->\n\n### ✅ 代码审查\n\n<div class=\'node-res